= Welcome =
The goal of this Noble Pursuit Games wiki is to provide a common repository and access point for all structured datum gathered either from the forums, the blog, or elsewhere.  This particular wiki is a highly customized version of the freely available perl-based UseMod wiki engine. 

== Topics ==
These are the principal starting points of this wiki. 

||TourBusStop||What to see and expect from this wiki, and how to contribute||
||CategoryPeople||Display links to all of the contributors of this wiki||
||GameDesignsInProgress||All games that are currently under consideration||
||SessionReports||Links to each set of after-action reports for playtesting||
||WikiEditing||Help on how to create new pages for this wiki||
||WikiStyleGuide||All editors of this wiki must adhere to the style guide||
||SandBox||A playground for messing with the wiki entries for n00bs||
||AdminFeatures||Certain editors will be l33t and have powerful tools available for them to mess things up||

